<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title> <%= title %> </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/adverts.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <section class="container-fluid content-row">
            <h1>Adverts</h1> 
            <div class="row">
            <%for(let i = 0; i < adverts.length; i++) {%>
                <article class="col-sm-3">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/<%=adverts[i].photo%>" alt="photo_<%= adverts[i].name %>">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title"><%= adverts[i].name %></h5>
                            <div class="card-subinfo">
                                <span class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted"> <%= adverts[i].for_sale ? 'For sale!' : 'Wanted!' %> </span>
                                <span class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted advert-price">$<%=adverts[i].price%></span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="card-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Illo incidunt numquam laborum commodi aspernatur laudantium rerum repellat? Rem saepe provident nihil quidem dignissimos quisquam adipisci, consequatur dolor ut assumenda! Quasi.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            <%}%>  
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>